Feature	Description	Example
Define function	name() { commands; } or function name {}	greet() { echo "Hi"; }
Call function	name [args]	greet Alice
Positional arguments	$1, $2, ..., $@, $#	echo $1
Return exit status	return n (0=success)	return 0
Return output	Use echo and capture with $(func)	result=$(add 1 2)
Local variables	local var=value	local x=5
Export functions	export -f name	export -f greet
Recursive functions	Functions that call themselves	factorial()
Check existence	declare -f funcname	declare -f greet